{"tid":1862233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護罷工必須一鼓作氣，不能有絲毫退縮","createTime":"2020-02-04T13:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T03:01:35.000Z","uid":217430,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d89343d2029796e284938a7fd4642af5ddbd3703","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"《左傳&middot;莊公十年》：「夫戰，勇氣也。一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。」<br />\n<br />\n古代作戰擊鼓進軍，擂第一通鼓時士氣最盛。後多喻趁銳氣旺盛之時一舉成事或鼓足幹勁，一往直前。<br />\n<br />\n全句意思是作戰是靠士兵的勇氣的。第一次擊鼓能夠振作士兵的勇氣，第二次擊鼓士兵的勇氣會衰弱，第三次擊鼓士兵的勇氣就竭盡了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工如是，今次醫護罷工行動必須一鼓作氣，不能對港共政府有絲毫讓步、退縮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">其他行業亦必須緊隨醫護手足的步伐，立即加入罷工。</span><br />\n<br />\n對敵人仁慈等於對香港人殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n我們已經緊緊渣住港共春袋，只須用力一握便能成事。這是千載難逢的機會，機不可失。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAABYKy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAABYKy.gif&h=0ffa8a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eQygwe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eQygwe.jpg&h=0835b748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護手足們，香港結局有兩：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1.全面封關，香港防疫成功，安然渡過危機。<br />\n<br />\n2.大開中門，香港成為武漢肺炎之收容港。醫療系統全面崩潰，港人患者無數。香港自此一蹶不振。</span><br />\n<br />\n一念之差將有折然不同的後果，望你們能堅持下去，而香港人奕會無限量支持你們。<br />\n一起做世界冠軍吧。<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0aBYRc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0aBYRc.jpg&h=c2ba09d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b133b0fb1723e784fabc53a42dffc792b934a58","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61d582349ac07b9d50f26cb96ba4c1f91a77ba8d","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6221ea65d9688412ed3e1a4de3bcee09f292164b","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"各行業請緊隨醫護手足的步伐。複製醫護罷工的成功方程式。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一.成立公會</span><br />\n並高調召開會員大會表決罷工，一定要有直播影著過程。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">二.開口牌</span><br />\n簽署罷工宣言承諾罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">三.全民醒覺</span><br />\n大家放心。已經有八成香港市民支持全面封關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>罷工救港<br />\n全面封關</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"89217861e3f3bad48a608f31230cd7ae66023867","tid":1862233,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"542d345f7f88a923f00c96f5fb17080a27224566","tid":1862233,"uid":203795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94a7e6270bfc697a0c174c928a656823c1136fce","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:50:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"063650dced19cc7fec8c71fc9f0457bc0a29e17a","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a540ab4f87bcb1b0f064be6d14106fe5bb61c1cf","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9175180a7aeb34c615e524af3266fc718c1a051","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b35a4a209d993cd995694640209da9b982a744c","tid":1862233,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"277e9676ff37d1569fd1d33efffa9e0148f65de8","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a967f0650553a4a9af094013e32d0d71db61608","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11f39404aafe07bafea4268cd6c79d7bba53ad7a","tid":1862233,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"[全民三罷] 醫護工會並不代表所有 醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1862232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1862232</a>"},{"pid":"0282764aea1ee57aefb8167d7b6e55170966af66","tid":1862233,"uid":85425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"三罷"},{"pid":"3830d87e1a063cc0086511884e13270255cc69fb","tid":1862233,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0282764aea1ee57aefb8167d7b6e55170966af66","tid":1862233,"uid":85425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"三罷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"對。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de75c786cac114afccdb9e8bfda8c5e32505090","tid":1862233,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"870e278620c0733a77923aa95ee87ff2bdb5477f","tid":1862233,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"不能對港共政府有絲毫讓步、退縮。<br />\n<br />\n其他行業亦必須緊隨醫護手足的步伐，立即加入罷工。"},{"pid":"449f560c17c060cb56fd88f3c850053b7fb2b199","tid":1862233,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"不能對港共政府有絲毫讓步、退縮。<br />\n<br />\n其他行業亦必須緊隨醫護手足的步伐，立即加入罷工。"},{"pid":"3c360aa4bf40e8d183969adfd3d173234e467236","tid":1862233,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"不能對港共政府有絲毫讓步、退縮。<br />\n<br />\n其他行業亦必須緊隨醫護手足的步伐，立即加入罷工。"},{"pid":"a8328eb5f469fcd9b5d135f94d5210e6a77ad7c5","tid":1862233,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":